flowchart LR

GitPush --> Static

Static --> Tests

Tests --> PromptEval

PromptEval --> RAGEval

RAGEval --> GuardrailEval

GuardrailEval --> Benchmarks

Benchmarks --> Metrics

Metrics --> Gate{Quality Gate}

Gate -- Pass --> Publish

Publish --> Deploy

Gate -- Fail --> HumanReview[Human Review]

HumanReview -- Approve --> Deploy

HumanReview -- Reject --> Block[Block Release]